Features introduced in OCaml 5.3 and that stdcompat should provide
backward support for, if only to say that they are not actually
supported.

## Features found in the OCaml Changes file for its release 5.3

- #13272: Allow maximum number of domains to be specified as a OCAMLRUNPARAM
  parameter.
